        },
        "bullet_point": {
            "value": [
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "HEROCLIP is the world's first 3-in-1 clip and hook that can hang just about anything, just about anywhere!",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "HANG STUFF SECURELY: Heroclip Large can hold up to 100 lbs and the rubber tip creates optimal grip so your stuff stays secure. 40% Larger than Medium.",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "COMPACT DESIGN: Hook and clip nest together when not in use. SIZE LARGE 4.1\" wide, 5.24\" high (closed)/7.25\" (expanded).",
                    "marketplace_id": "ATVPDKIKX0DER"
                },
                {
                    "language_tag": "en_US",
                    "value": "COUNTLESS USES: Our Large Heroclip is ideal for bulky outdoor gear, garage organization, shopping carts, strollers and much more.",
